title: A-Z Databases
cleaned_text: Licensing restrictions limit database access to current University of Tasmania students and staff. [Passwords to access Library electronic resources](https://www.utas.edu.au/library/find/databases/databases-passwords): a small number of databases require a username and password other than your personal authentication in order to gain access.
